{"data":[{"date":"22:33 06/08","title":"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ef1 ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/6/tien-ve-hung-dung-lo-lang-ve-kha-nang-du-asiad.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u2013 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ASIAD c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nH\u00f9ng D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Oman v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u00e1t n\u00fat v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0, b\u1eb1ng si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;t\u00e2n binh&rdquo; \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 sau l\u01b0ng, c\u1ea7m nh\u1ecbp tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 trong danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 Olympic, Mr. Park bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i 1 trong 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean qu\u00e1 23 tu\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, V\u0103n L\u00e2m, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c. N\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec1u ra qu\u00e2n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/hung.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh n\u00e0o. D\u00f9 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng hay kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a \u0110T v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c th\u00f4i. V\u0103n L\u00e2m, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean t\u00f4i trong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp. C\u00f2n danh s\u00e1ch cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng g\u1ed3m 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1edfi BHL y\u00eau c\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y Park: &ldquo;HLV \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 d\u1ea1y t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ASIAD.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ly-do-u23-viet-nam-da-hai-tran-da-chinh-thuc-vo-dich-168-193812.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/ly-do-u23-viet-nam-da-hai-tran-da-chinh-thuc-vo-dich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ly-do-u23-viet-nam-da-hai-tran-da-chinh-thuc-vo-dich-168-193812.html\">L\u00fd do U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1edbm ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi hai th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine v\u00e0 Oman, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap c\u00f9ng ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 ngh\u00ecn \u0111\u00f4 la cho m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-u23-viet-nam-10-u23-oman-chien-thang-cua-su-can-dam-168-193810.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/du-am-u23-viet-nam-10-u23-oman-chien-thang-cua-su-can-dam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-u23-viet-nam-10-u23-oman-chien-thang-cua-su-can-dam-168-193810.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U23 Oman: Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 can \u0111\u1ea3m</span><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u01b0\u1eddng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1 th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i khi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5171","checkdouble":"193884"},{"date":"20:19 06/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 6/8: M.U nh\u1eafm 3 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-68-mu-nham-3-trung-ve-den-han-chot-phien-cho-he.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 6/8.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U nh\u1eafm 3 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf mu\u1ed1n \u0111em v\u1ec1 1 trong 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 theo th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 \u01b0u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 Jerome Boateng, Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld. 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, 75 tri\u1ec7u v\u00e0 60 tri\u1ec7u. Mourinho d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n xoay sang s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 trung v\u1ec7 trong m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 68 MU nh\u1eafm 3 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 68 MU nh\u1eafm 3 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/ngay-hom-nay-68.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 6/8: M.U nh\u1eafm 3 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t TTCN</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Arsenal t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i y\u00eau s\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Ramsey<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales, b\u1edfi anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi CLB. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00fac m\u1eafc c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 2 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng, khi Aaron Ramsey \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1edbi 300 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Chelsea \u0111ang t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o ng\u00f4i sao Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sarri b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh \u0111\u1ec3 Courtois ra \u0111i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1edbt l\u1edd nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Courtois, v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee3i \u00fd r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Chelsea n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Willian ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Courtois, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng t\u00e2n HLV Sarri. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Willian c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi h\u1ecfi mua ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 6/8 \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Willian r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Firmino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/willian-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-va-real-madrid.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 6/8: Willian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u00e1m tr\u1ee5 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf Arsenal<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Lucas Perez, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang b\u1ecb l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean t\u1ea1i Emirates mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i CLB b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, sau kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian b\u1ecb \u0111em \u0111i cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Perez \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua t\u1eeb Sporting v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, v\u00e0 HLV Emery v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5170","checkdouble":"193875"},{"date":"22:25 06/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a MU sau tr\u1eadn thua Bayern","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/6/nhung-diem-tich-cuc-va-han-che-cua-mu-sau-tran-thua-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c khi ch\u1ec9 tung ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy nh\u1ea5t 1 c\u00fa s\u00fat v\u1ec1 khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Bayern trong su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a MU sau tr\u1eadn thua Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a MU sau tr\u1eadn thua Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Nhung-diem-tich-cuc-va-han-che-cua-MU-sau-tran-thua-Bayern-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Darmian t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec1u k\u00e9m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Franck Ribery v\u00e0 Arjen Robben c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 69. Nh\u01b0ng hai l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n g\u00ec khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb sung m\u00e3n b\u00ean ph\u00eda Man United l\u00e0 Darmian v\u00e0 Shaw.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng xu\u1ed1ng bi\u00ean c\u1ee7a &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Robben v\u00e0 Thiago Alcantara x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede Premier League, Man United ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00e1nh \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. V\u00e0 tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang bi\u00ean c\u1ee7a MU c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 trong tr\u1eadn thua 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac Man United ph\u1ea3i lao v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Man City \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i khi mang v\u1ec1 Kyle Walker v\u00e0 Benjamin Mendy. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn gi\u00fap Man xanh c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep Guardiola.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bailly v\u00e0 Lindelof g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bailly\" title=\"Bailly\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/221913-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Bailly v\u1eefng nh\u01b0 b\u00e0n th\u1ea1ch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u00f9ng nhau v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Man United. Trong 416 ng\u00e0y k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Lindelof c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Man United, anh m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f9ng Bailly \u0111\u00fang 1 l\u1ea7n trong h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 Smalling.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 HLV Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Allianz Arena. Kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 Lewandowski. B\u1edfi Bailly \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Lewandowski \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Thomas Muller c\u00e2m l\u1eb7ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1eeb tay Smalling v\u00e0 Jones. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu Man \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Toby Alderweireld th\u00ec c\u1eb7p Bailly &ndash; Lindelof n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Rashford tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rashford\" title=\"Rashford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/221922-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Rashford th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marcus Rashford \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u1edf m\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRashford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1edfi Mata v\u00e0 Sanchez \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-10-mu-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-329-193818.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bayern vs MU</span>. Anh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ng\u00e1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Hummels v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c th\u1eafng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Man United kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Rashford. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y s\u1ebd g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng MU v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u00e1o huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a s\u00e2n Old Trafford tr\u00ean l\u01b0ng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u00c1p l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn cho Woodward</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man United l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u00ec l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Mourinho th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o CEO Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf r\u1eb1ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a MU l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 d\u00f9 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 ti\u1ec1n t\u1ea5n v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Ed Woodward c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Mourinho v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 b\u1ec1 sa th\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch k\u00e9m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, kh\u00f3 HLV n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Premier League hay Champions League v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p t\u1ea1i Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nguy-khon-mourinho-gui-loi-cau-cuu-hoc-tro-172-193830.html\">M.U nguy kh\u1ed1n, Mourinho g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-ti-nanh-voi-cac-doi-thu-khong-ngung-voi-vinh-bld-man-utd-172-193823.html\">MU thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c Bayern, Mourinho ra t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 cho gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-10-mu-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-329-193818.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Bayern Munich 1-0 MU (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5169","checkdouble":"193883"},{"date":"21:00 06/08","title":"Kroos: \u201cQu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/kroos-qua-kho-de-thay-the-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng, Real Madrid s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nKroos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 CR7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, thi \u0111\u1ea5u 438 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 450 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng &ndash; Cris Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c d\u1ee9t \u00e1o ra \u0111i v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi Real Madrid, d\u00f9 h\u1ecd thu v\u1ec1 h\u01a1n 100 tri\u1ec7u euro ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/m\u00f9a nh\u01b0 si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng ch\u1edd xem CLB s\u1ebd l\u00e0m g\u00ec. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p con s\u1ed1 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/m\u00f9a m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, Ronaldo \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. D\u00f9 sao, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1ec1 CLB c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/5/3/Tien-ve-Toni-Kroos-tiec-nuoi-ve-su-ra-di-cua-Ronaldo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kroos ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Luka Modric &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n sang Inter Milan, Kroos cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Luka t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1edbi nhau 4 n\u0103m r\u1ed3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 HLV Julen Lopetegui, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;T\u00f4i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 tu\u1ea7n, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 bi\u1ebft Lopetegui tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Lopetegui s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho Real Madrid.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Kroos ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Los Blancos s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Hi\u1ec7n nay, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 bom t\u1ea5n n\u00e0o, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/4-ly-do-tin-rang-los-blancos-se-sup-do-o-mua-giai-toi-180-192418.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/4-ly-do-tin-rang-los-blancos-se-sup-do-o-mua-giai-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/4-ly-do-tin-rang-los-blancos-se-sup-do-o-mua-giai-toi-180-192418.html\">4 l\u00fd do tin r\u1eb1ng Los Blancos s\u1ebd s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t \u1edf th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao v\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do Real Madrid s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u00f9a...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muc-luong-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-o-juventus-khung-khiep-den-the-nao-176-193834.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/muc-luong-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-o-juventus-khung-khiep-den-the-nao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muc-luong-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-o-juventus-khung-khiep-den-the-nao-176-193834.html\">M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf Juventus kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?</span><br>\r\nM\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo thu\u1ed9c h\u00e0ng top th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 so v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng chung \u1edf Serie A, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f2n th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 Juventus ch\u1ecbu ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5168","checkdouble":"193878"},{"date":"06:39 07/08","title":"Real Madrid ch\u1ed1t 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Modric","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/real-madrid-chot-70-trieu-euro-cho-nguoi-thay-the-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic thay Luka Modric, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuka Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018, ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua Ph\u00e1p 2-4.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric Real\" title=\"Modric Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/10/13/Deco-Chi-1-cau-thu-Real-du-trinh-khoac-ao-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 33 anh v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 5 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Modric, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn M.U, Chelsea hay Inter Milan. Trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, Inter l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ecf ra quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 45 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Modric.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Modric, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 750 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Inter Milan g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia v\u1eabn \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Los Blancos b\u00e1n c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real nh\u1eafm Miralem Pjanic thay Modric</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic thay Luka Modric, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic thay Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic thay Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/24/Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Miralem-Pjanic-thay-Luka-Modric-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real nh\u1eafm Pjanic thay Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia c\u0169ng duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea5t\u00a0c\u1ee7a Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, Pjanic ho\u00e0n t\u00f2an c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Modric \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, song thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Juventus b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n Higuain, Juventus quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pjanic. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Real d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9ng 70 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Real \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng Juventus s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u1ea3 Pjanic.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pjanic, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-muc-tieu-200-trieu-euro-thay-modric-180-193772.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real mua Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a Tottenham</span>, Los Blancos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra 200 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5167","checkdouble":"193890"},{"date":"05:52 07/08","title":"Atletico \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/2/atletico-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-tien-dao-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Atletico Madrid mua Nikola Kalinic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, theo Gianluca Di Marzio \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid s\u1eafp c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb AC Milan.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Kevin Gameiro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKevin Gameiro c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Atletico Madrid t\u1eeb Sevilla v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid sau chu\u1ed7i phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Atletico Madrid mua Nikola Kalinic c\u1ee7a AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Atletico Madrid mua Nikola Kalinic c\u1ee7a AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/23/Atletico-Madrid-mua-Nikola-Kalinic-cua-AC-Milan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kevin Gameiro s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Valencia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i ra s\u00e2n 59 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 19 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n anh \u0111\u1ec3 mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nValencia \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Kevin Gameiro, theo Don Balon, \u201cB\u1ea7y d\u01a1i\u201d \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro. Hi\u1ec7n\u00a0Rojiblancos \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 c\u1ef1u sao Sevilla.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/atletico-muon-co-giroud-tu-chelsea-172-191744.html\" target=\"_blank\">Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Giroud</span>, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Michy Batshuayi, song Chelsea d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Hi\u1ec7n Atletico \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Atletico \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Nikola Kalinic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Atletico Madrid mua Nikola Kalinic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, theo Gianluca Di Marzio \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid s\u1eafp c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb AC Milan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nicola Kalinic nhieu kha nang se ngoi du bi cho Higuain\" title=\"Nicola Kalinic nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Higuain\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/atletico-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-tien-dao-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Atletico \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Nicola Kalinic\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb Giroud v\u00e0 Batshuayi, Atletico \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Nikola Kalinic c\u1ee7a AC Milan. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGianluca Di Marzio kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Atletico \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 15 tri\u1ec7u euro, m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 ghi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 30 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c AC Milan mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Gonzalo Higuain, Kalinic r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i. C\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Atletico ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Diego Costa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5166","checkdouble":"193893"},{"date":"22:17 06/08","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn cho th\u1ea5y M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/day-dau-hieu-cuc-lon-cho-thay-mu-chuan-bi-don-trung-ve-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, trung v\u1ec7 Axel Tuanzebe r\u1eddi M.U d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, m\u1edf ra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ed5 sung \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSao tr\u1ebb Tuanzebe ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111i du h\u1ecdc<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Aston Villa d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 5 tr\u1eadn v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Villa, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau khi g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Fulham trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft play-off h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng N\u0103m, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do h\u1ecd t\u00e1i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Tuanzebe.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda M.U \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ra \u0111i m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, \u0111\u1ec3 thu th\u1eadp kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t. Axel Tuanzebe \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u00f9ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jose Mourinho \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i, sao tr\u1ebb cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quay l\u1ea1i Villa. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn v\u00e0 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m vinh d\u1ef1 khi m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi t\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Sao tr\u1ebb Axel Tuanzebe r\u1eddi MU d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Sao tr\u1ebb Axel Tuanzebe r\u1eddi MU d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/tuan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Axel Tuanzebe r\u1eddi M.U, t\u1edbi Aston Villa d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 m\u1eafc n\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u00fat nghi ng\u1edd n\u00e0o, t\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho su\u1ea5t th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng Premier League. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i&rdquo; &ndash; Tuanzebe cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c sao tr\u1ebb AxelTuanzebe r\u1eddi M.U, anh l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 5 ra \u0111i d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, sau nh\u1eefng Joel Pereira (t\u1edbi Vitoria Setubal), Dean Henderson (Sheffield United), Cameron Borthwick-Jackson (Scunthorpe United) v\u00e0 Matty Willock (St Mirren).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, \u0111\u00e2y d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 Jose Mourinho b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, Man United \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n nhanh ch\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Jerome Boateng t\u1eeb Bayern Munich.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-pogba-da-tro-lai-man-united-172-193880.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/6/chinh-thuc-pogba-da-tro-lai-man-united.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-pogba-da-tro-lai-man-united-172-193880.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United</span><br>\r\nSau khi tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y l\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-boateng-voi-mu-172-193871.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/arsenal-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-boateng-voi-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-boateng-voi-mu-172-193871.html\">Arsenal gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi M.U</span><br>\r\nArsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5165","checkdouble":"193882"},{"date":"06:06 07/08","title":"Willian nh\u1eafn Mourinho: \"T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi \u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e2y gi\u1edd\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/5/28/Willian-tu-choi-kheo-loi-moi-toi-MU-cua-thay-cu-Mourinho-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Mourinho nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Willian \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Mourinho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian \u1edf Chelsea. Trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng nhau, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian Mourinho\" title=\"Willian Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/12/23/HLV-Jose-Mourinho-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willian \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao HLV Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 trong nhi\u1ec7m k\u1ef3 th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf Chelsea, Willian l\u00e0 Matic l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 55 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Willian \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Mourinho, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean nh\u1eafn tin v\u1edbi nhau.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\"Mourinho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng HLV gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u00f4i khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n,\u00a0c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u00fac ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eafn tin, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1eedi tin nh\u1eafn cho nhau th\u00f4ng qua WhatsApp\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u00d4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00edch mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Mourinho m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.\"</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Willian h\u1eb9n Mourinho trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tu-choi-ban-willian-cho-barca-nhung-mu-thi-khac-172-189983.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Willian</span>, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n Man \u0111\u1ecf chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Mourinho nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn MU \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn MU \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Willian-noi-ve-viec-chuyen-den-MU-o-ky-chuyen-nhuong-He-2018-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willian h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Mourinho th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft M.U c\u00f3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea hay kh\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cMourinho ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi M.U, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n m\u00ecnh hay kh\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i th\u00edch s\u1ed1ng \u1edf London, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch s\u1ed1ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00ec v\u1eady, v\u00e2ng, t\u00f4i \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u1eaft HLV m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5164","checkdouble":"193889"},{"date":"05:37 07/08","title":"C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/cuc-nong-mu-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 khi Tottenham mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7 thay th\u1ebf.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Toby Alderweireld</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca, M.U \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed1i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Toby Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Toby Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/cuc-nong-mu-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Alderweireld</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Goal, MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 Spurs \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Tottenham mu\u1ed1n 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f2n M.U ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u00e0 theo ngu\u1ed3n tin \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb Goal, hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Alderweireld kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Tottenham, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn anh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Spurs v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. HLV Pochettino kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao Tottenham t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi M.U v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 6 v\u1eeba qua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, khi m\u00e0 Alderweireld \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00ec Tottenham bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Alderweireld s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn M.U ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c n\u1ebfu...</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham m\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn b\u00e1n Alderweireld cho M.U, song h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Hi\u1ec7n Spurs \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Atletico.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Lascelles\" title=\"hau ve Lascelles\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/leicester-hoi-mua-lascelles-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham nh\u1eafm Lascelles thay Alderweireld\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJamaal Lascelles c\u1ee7a Newcastle v\u00e0 Matthijs de Ligt c\u1ee7a Ajax l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Tottenham nh\u1eafm thay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Alderweireld v\u1edbi Tottenham ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m, trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 12 th\u00e1ng, ng\u00f4i\u00a0sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ra \u0111i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2019, M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n b\u1ecf ra 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alderweireld, song Mourinho kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i l\u00e2u h\u01a1n. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n nhanh ch\u00f3ng mua th\u00eam \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cuc-lon-cho-thay-mu-chuan-bi-don-trung-ve-moi-172-193882.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU \u0111\u1ec3 Axel Tuanzebe t\u1edbi Aston Villa </span>theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5163","checkdouble":"193891"},{"date":"05:21 07/08","title":"Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Real b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/courtois-tu-choi-tro-lai-chelsea-quyet-tam-den-real-bang-duoc.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong khi Hazard, Giroud v\u00e0 Kante \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Courtois v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi Man City, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2. Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man xanh, The Blues \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Thibaut-Courtois-muon-roi-Chelsea-toi-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng Chelsea nh\u01b0ng Courtois th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf Cobham, nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 Eden Hazard, Olivier Giroud v\u00e0 N'Golo Kante \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau qu\u00e3ng ngh\u1ec9 sau World Cup 2018. B\u1ed9 ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau khi h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y n\u00e9t m\u1eb7t vui v\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri khi \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Theo t\u1edd Telegraph, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge, anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u1edf B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft khi n\u00e0o s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i London \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real Madrid \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/courtois-tu-choi-tro-lai-chelsea-quyet-tam-den-real-bang-duoc.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois v\u1eabn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nguoi-dai-dien-cau-xin-chelsea-hay-buong-tha-cho-courtois-172-193720.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois</span>, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea7u xin Chelsea bu\u00f4ng tha cho th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i TBN \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng Chelsea l\u1ea1i ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Courtois c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Real Madrid thi \u0111\u1ea5u, song ph\u00eda Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Hi\u1ec7n h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJan Oblak v\u00e0 Jack Butland \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 hai trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea nh\u1eafm thay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa Oblak v\u00e0 Atletico c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Stoke \u0111\u00f2i 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Butland.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5162","checkdouble":"193892"},{"date":"06:52 07/08","title":"MU ch\u1ed1t 120 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/1/3/mu-chot-120-trieu-euro-cho-nguoi-thay-the-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mua Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Paul Pogba chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang nh\u1eafm Paul Pogba nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Iniesta \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Camp Nou b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 120 tri\u1ec7u euro, MU mua Milinkovic-Savic thay Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 120 tri\u1ec7u euro, MU mua Milinkovic-Savic thay Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Chi-120-trieu-euro,-MU-mua-Milinkovic-Savic-thay-Paul-Pogba-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Pogba m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi t\u1edbi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Mino Raiola c\u1ee7a Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi M.U v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t,&nbsp;Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U sau qu\u00e3ng ngh\u1ec9 sau World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 M.U v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, Pogba mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed y\u00eau th\u00edch, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng anh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU nh\u1eafm Milinkovic-Savic thay Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo CalcioMercato.com, MU mua Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Paul Pogba chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/milinkovicsavic-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU nh\u1eafm Milinkovic-Savic thay Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chi-120-trieu-euro-ac-milan-tinh-vuot-mat-mu-vu-pogba-serbia-172-193722.html\" target=\"_blank\">AC Milan mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic</span>, song l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Lazio th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho Real v\u00e0 Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia. Theo CalcioMercato.com, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 120 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMilinkovic-Savic \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia ghi t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n \u1edf Serie A, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5161","checkdouble":"193895"},{"date":"14:23 06/08","title":"B\u1ea1n g\u00e1i Sergio Ramos khoe d\u00e1ng \u0111\u1eb9p 4 th\u00e1ng sau sinh","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/ban-gai-sergio-ramos-khoe-dang-dep-4-thang-sau-sinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Pilar Rubio di\u1ec7n bikini g\u00e2y ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean cho c\u00e1c fan khi l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i v\u00f3c d\u00e1ng nhanh sau khi sinh con.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\"4 th\u00e1ng sau khi con trai Alejandro ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi, b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i Sergio Ramos xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c trong h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u00f4 m\u1eb7c bikini \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ea1nh c\u00e2y c\u1ecd\", t\u1edd AS b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn. H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee5p trong chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 m\u00e1t t\u1ea1i khu b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n Sian Ka'an c\u1ee7a Mexico. Pilar Rubio v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111i x\u1ea3 h\u01a1i b\u00ean nhau sau khi World Cup k\u1ebft th\u00fac. T\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 n\u00e0y, Sergio Ramos c\u1ea7u h\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00ecnh v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ea1n g\u00e1i Sergio Ramos khoe d\u00e1ng \u0111\u1eb9p 4 th\u00e1ng sau sinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ea1n g\u00e1i Sergio Ramos khoe d\u00e1ng \u0111\u1eb9p 4 th\u00e1ng sau sinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/cc-2888-1533434826.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pilar Rubio v\u1eeba c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n trai \u1edf Mexico. \u1ea2nh: Instagram.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i video tr\u00ean k\u00eanh YouTube c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 v\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng HLV Noe Todea \u0111\u1ec3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Pilar Rubio nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. Kh\u00f4ng \u00edt fan ghen t\u1ef5 v\u1edbi th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 d\u00f9 m\u1edbi ch\u1eeda \u0111\u1ebb. \"Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 tin \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u00e0 m\u1eb9 \u0111ang c\u00f3 con 4 th\u00e1ng tu\u1ed5i\", \"Sergio Ramos qu\u00e1 may m\u1eafn v\u00ec c\u00f3 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i xinh \u0111\u1eb9p, b\u1ed1c l\u1eeda\"... l\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a fan b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5160","checkdouble":"193847"},{"date":"14:25 06/08","title":"C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Seedorf khoe c\u01a1 b\u1eafp cu\u1ed3n cu\u1ed9n","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/cuu-danh-thu-seedorf-khoe-co-bap-cuon-cuon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marcelo, Puyol hay Roberto Carlos \u0111\u1ec1u ng\u1ee1 ng\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Seedorf.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br>\r\n\"Clarence Seedorf b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\", t\u1edd AS b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00e0 Lan chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8, trong \u0111\u00f3 anh ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n. Th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Seedorf nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 b\u1eafp, khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 c\u00e1c danh th\u1ee7, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 x\u00f4n xao b\u00e0n t\u00e1n ngay t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/cc-2318-1533521888.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u00e2n c\u1ecf 5 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, anh l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Cameroon.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i c\u1edb \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1eebng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 d\u00f9 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd ng\u1eebng ch\u01a1i th\u1ec3 thao \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t, tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vui\", c\u1ef1u sao Real Madrid ch\u00fa th\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1eadu h\u01a1i l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo. C\u1eadu c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n\", Carles Puyol d\u00ed d\u1ecfm b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn. \"\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n\", \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Van Hooijdonk vi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"C\u00e1i g\u00ec th\u1ebf\", Marcelo th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean. Anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil duy nh\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn. C\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Roberto Carlos c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f9a gi\u1ee1n: \"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh n\u00e0y t\u1eeb 8 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ed3i\" khi\u1ebfn Dani Alves ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn: \"Roberto qu\u00e1 v\u00f4 l\u00fd\".</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5159","checkdouble":"193848"}]}